# Generated Impact-T deck if ever written in-tree (the linac_rest stage runs in
# lume-impact's temp workdir, so this is belt-and-suspenders). NOTE: do NOT add a
# blanket `rfdata*` ignore — the vendored TW field shapes in linac_rest/rfdata/ are
# committed source and must stay tracked.
